updates.title: VAICOM PRO Community Edition for DCS World
updates.releasenotes: Expands AI_ATC keywords to include Vector endpoints and corrects previous errors with tower endpoints, Adds new F10 Menu Import Known Aliases for community Scripts, Moose, Hound, AI_ATC etc. **You will need to do the finish step to add them to your profile** Import F10 menus must be selected on for them to work.
